        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><strong>BODE Index</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>4-year survival</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>0&ndash;2</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>80%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>3&ndash;4</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>67%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>5&ndash;6</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>57%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>7&ndash;10</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>18%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Survival estimates based on Kaplan-Meier curves from <a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa021322#t=article\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Celli 2004</a>:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/content/bodeindex-curves.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>",
